data.description: Welcome to your home in the heart of the New Center area! This charming brick 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts an inviting open floor plan. Step inside to discover a spacious livingwith plenty of natural light, seamlessly flowing into the kitchen. With ample counter space and a convenient pantry, meal preparation becomes quick and easy. The three generously sized bedrooms offer relaxation and privacy, perfect for both family living and hosting guests. Enjoy breathtaking views from the comfort of your own home. Convenience is key, with easy access to local town amenities and a plethora of dining options nearby. Plus, the excitement of Pigeon Forge and Gatlinburg, along with their myriad attractions, are just a quick drive away. Entertain effortlessly on the back deck, complete with storage space underneath. With a 2-car garage, this residence offers everything you need for modern living in a highly desirable location. This property does need some TLC to make it your own.
